title: Dede T03  (2015) (Savages-Empire) cbr
description:
"Just get ne the object back."
Monsieur Rochmann, big cheese at the Louvre in Paris, is missing a mummy.
And while neither the strange circumstances of its disappearance nor a
malicious murder attempt on his person or the realization that he's not
the only one searching for the mummy are able to scare Dede off the case,
a most disturbing thought is starting to rob him of his sleep: What if the
object he is searching is actually alive?

enjoy
